data.description: Recently built in 2020, this craftsman style home offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Upon entering, you will be greeted by a spacious and inviting living area with an abundance of natural light and a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and modern kitchen, which boasts granite countertops, ample cabinet space and pantry for additional storage. On the main level you will find three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, including a master suite with trey ceilings, ensuite bathroom and generously sized walk in closet. Each bedroom is thoughtfully designed with ample closet space and large windows allowing plenty of natural light. Just a few steps down in the daylight basement is a generously sized bonus room and an additional full bathroom. Enjoy the outdoors from the back deck overlooking the large, fenced in backyard, perfect for outdoor entertaining. The home is conveniently located in the Sedman Hills community, just a short drive from all of Hixson's shopping and restaurants. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful home yours!
